## Part 2: Interactive Memoria Menu

### Activation
- **Keybind**: Hold 'M' or dedicated button
- **Effect**: Time slows (similar to VATS/Tac-Scan)
- **Visual**: World desaturates, Memoria interface expands to center screen

### Menu Structure

#### Main Interface
```
╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║           MEMORIA CONSULTATION SUITE          ║
╠═══════════════════════════════════════════════╣
║                                               ║
║  [1] Tactical Analysis                        ║
║  [2] Bestiary & Enemy Intel                   ║
║  [3] Environmental Scan                       ║
║  [4] Mission Guidance                         ║
║  [5] Network & Communications                 ║
║  [6] Memoria Settings                         ║
║  [7] Conversation                             ║
║                                               ║
╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════╝
```

#### 1. Tactical Analysis
**Purpose**: Deep dive into current combat situation

**Features**:
- 3D battlefield visualization with enemy positions
- Suggested tactics based on loadout
- Environmental hazards mapped
- Optimal positioning recommendations
- Escape route highlighting

**Example Display**:
```
╔═ TACTICAL OVERVIEW ═══════════════════════════╗
║ Current Situation: AMBUSH                     ║
║ Hostiles: 5 (3 Melee, 2 Ranged)              ║
║ Cover Positions: 3 available                  ║
║                                               ║
║ RECOMMENDED ACTION:                           ║
║ "Fall back to chokepoint, use Shield Ward    ║
║  to block arrows while engaging melee."       ║
║                                               ║
║ SUCCESS PROBABILITY: 67% (with cover)         ║
╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════╝
```

#### 2. Bestiary & Enemy Intel
**Purpose**: Detailed enemy database

**Features**:
- Scrollable list of encountered enemies
- Detailed stats, weaknesses, resistances
- Behavioral patterns
- Drop tables and loot information
- Combat tips and strategies
- Lore entries (unlocked through observation)

**Example Entry**:
```
╔═ GHOUL ═══════════════════════════════════════╗
║ Classification: Undead Humanoid               ║
║ Threat Level: ★★★☆☆                          ║
║ Encounters: 47                                ║
║                                               ║
║ PHYSICAL ATTRIBUTES:                          ║
║ Health: High | Stamina: Medium                ║
║ Speed: Slow | Detection: Moderate             ║
║                                               ║
║ RESISTANCES:                                  ║
║ ████████░░ Slash (80%)                        ║
║ ██████░░░░ Pierce (60%)                       ║
║ ███░░░░░░░ Blunt (30%)                        ║
║ ██░░░░░░░░ Fire (20%)                         ║
║                                               ║
║ BEHAVIORAL PATTERNS:                          ║
║ - Aggressive on sight                         ║
║ - Groups: 2-5 individuals                     ║
║ - Peak activity: Nighttime                    ║
║                                               ║
║ MEMORIA NOTES:                                ║
║ "Hardy creatures requiring excessive force.   ║
║  Recommend bludgeoning weapons or fire magic. ║
║  Target head for critical damage."            ║
╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════╝
```

#### 3. Environmental Scan
**Purpose**: Analyze surroundings for hazards, resources, points of interest

**Features**:
- Treasure/resource detection (limited by Memoria energy)
- Trap identification and disarm suggestions
- Hidden passage detection
- Material analysis (for crafting)
- Weather and time-based warnings

**Example Display**:
```
╔═ ENVIRONMENTAL SCAN ══════════════════════════╗
║ Location: Ancient Ruins - North Wing          ║
║ Energy Cost: ⚡⚡░░░ (2/5)                     ║
║                                               ║
║ DETECTED:                                     ║
║ ⚠ Pressure Plate (3m ahead)                   ║
║   └─ Disarm: Lockpick 45+                     ║
║ ◉ Herb Cluster (Wild Sage x3)                 ║
║ ◈ Weak Wall (destructible)                    ║
║ ◎ Chest (locked, difficulty: medium)          ║
║                                               ║
║ ENVIRONMENTAL HAZARDS:                        ║
║ - Structural instability: 45%                 ║
║ - Toxic spores detected (low concentration)   ║
║                                               ║
║ RECOMMENDATION:                               ║
║ "Proceed with caution. Recommend antidote     ║
║  preparation before exploring deeper."        ║
╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════╝
```

#### 4. Mission Guidance
**Purpose**: Quest tracking and strategic advice

**Features**:
- Active quest list with priorities
- Objective markers and waypoint management
- Time-sensitive quest warnings
- Consequence predictions for major decisions
- Alternative approach suggestions

**Example Display**:
```
╔═ ACTIVE MISSIONS ═════════════════════════════╗
║                                               ║
║ ⦿ PRIMARY: The Lost Archive                   ║
║   └─ Find Scholar Moren's research notes      ║
║   └─ Time Remaining: 2 days, 14 hours ⏱      ║
║   └─ Memoria Advice: "Urgent. Prioritize."   ║
║                                               ║
║ ○ SECONDARY: Merchant's Request               ║
║   └─ Deliver package to Tradetown             ║
║   └─ Reward: 150 gold                         ║
║                                               ║
║ ◎ SEEKER GUILD: Ghoul Nest Clearing           ║
║   └─ Eliminate 15 ghouls (7/15)               ║
║   └─ Co-op available (ping allies)            ║
║                                               ║
║ CONSEQUENCE WARNING:                          ║
║ "Failure to complete 'Lost Archive' may      ║
║  result in faction reputation loss."          ║
╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════╝
```

#### 5. Network & Communications
**Purpose**: Seeker Guild coordination and multiplayer features

**Features**:
- Nearby Seekers list with status
- Send distress signals / request backup
- Share enemy intel and map data
- Guild mission board
- Voice chat integration
- Friend list and party management

**Example Display**:
```
╔═ SEEKER NETWORK ══════════════════════════════╗
║ Connection: STABLE                            ║
║ Guild Rank: Adept Seeker                      ║
║                                               ║
║ NEARBY SEEKERS (3):                           ║
║ ◉ "Kael" - Level 18 - [120m, NE]             ║
║   └─ Status: In Combat                        ║
║   └─ [Offer Assistance]                       ║
║                                               ║
║ ◉ "Lyra" - Level 22 - [340m, S]              ║
║   └─ Status: Exploring                        ║
║                                               ║
║ ◉ "Daren" - Level 15 - [580m, W]             ║
║   └─ Status: Idle (Town)                      ║
║                                               ║
║ DISTRESS CALLS (1):                           ║
║ ⚠ "Kael" requests backup!                     ║
║   └─ [Join] [Decline] [Send Gear]            ║
║                                               ║
║ GUILD BOARD (2 new missions):                 ║
║ • Elite Hunt: Wendigo Sighting                ║
║ • Resource Run: Silver Ore x20                ║
╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════╝
```

#### 6. Memoria Settings
**Purpose**: Customize AI behavior and interface

**Features**:
- Alert frequency (High/Medium/Low/Off)
- Voice line frequency
- HUD position and scale
- Personality tuning (Tactical/Friendly/Minimal)
- Auto-scan options
- Energy regeneration rate (tied to equipment upgrades)

**Example Display**:
```
╔═ MEMORIA CONFIGURATION ═══════════════════════╗
║                                               ║
║ INTERFACE:                                    ║
║ • HUD Position: [Top Right] ▼                 ║
║ • HUD Scale: [━━━━●─────] 60%                ║
║ • Opacity: [━━━━━━●───] 70%                  ║
║                                               ║
║ BEHAVIOR:                                     ║
║ • Alert Level: [High] [●Medium] [Low]        ║
║ • Voice Lines: [All] [●Combat Only] [Off]    ║
║ • Personality: [●Tactical] [Friendly] [Minimal]
║ • Auto-Scan: [●Enabled] [Disabled]           ║
║                                               ║
║ ADVANCED:                                     ║
║ • Enemy Detection Range: 50m                  ║
║ • Energy Regen Rate: +2/sec (upgrade: +4)    ║
║ • Bestiary Auto-Update: ●Enabled             ║
║                                               ║
╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════╝
```

#### 7. Conversation
**Purpose**: Roleplay interaction with Memoria AI

**Features**:
- Dialogue options to ask questions
- Lore and backstory about Memoria Engines
- Relationship building (affects AI personality over time)
- Easter eggs and humor
- Training mode (tutorials)

**Example Interaction**:
```
╔═ MEMORIA DIALOGUE ════════════════════════════╗
║                                               ║
║ MEMORIA:                                      ║
║ "Seeker, you have a question. I am           ║
║  listening."                                  ║
║                                               ║
║ CHOOSE TOPIC:                                 ║
║ [1] Tell me about yourself                    ║
║ [2] What are the Memoria Engines?             ║
║ [3] How can I improve your capabilities?      ║
║ [4] Do you ever get bored?                    ║
║ [5] Combat training request                   ║
║ [6] Nevermind                                 ║
║                                               ║
╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════╝
```

